### ============ Health ============

### Gateway health (expect UP with db details)
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Account Service health
GET http://localhost:8081/health


### ============ Happy path ============

### Submit a new event (expect 201, status PENDING)
POST http://localhost:8080/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt-001",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "CREDIT",
  "amount": 150.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:02:11Z",
  "metadata": {
    "source": "mainframe-batch",
    "batchId": "B-9042"
  }
}

### ============ Idempotency ============

### Submit the EXACT same event again (expect 200, same body, no new row)
POST http://localhost:8080/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt-001",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "CREDIT",
  "amount": 150.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:02:11Z",
  "metadata": {
    "source": "mainframe-batch",
    "batchId": "B-9042"
  }
}

### Same eventId, DIFFERENT amount (expect 409 Conflict)
POST http://localhost:8080/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt-001",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "CREDIT",
  "amount": 999.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:02:11Z"
}


### ============ Out-of-order arrival ============

### Later business time, arrives first
POST http://localhost:8080/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt-003",
  "accountId": "acct-777",
  "type": "DEBIT",
  "amount": 25.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T15:00:00Z"
}

### Earlier business time, arrives second
POST http://localhost:8080/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt-002",
  "accountId": "acct-777",
  "type": "CREDIT",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:00:00Z"
}

### List events (expect evt-002 FIRST — chronological, not arrival order)
GET http://localhost:8080/events?account=acct-777


### ============ Retrieval ============

### Get one event by id
GET http://localhost:8080/events/evt-001

### Unknown event (expect 404 with message)
GET http://localhost:8080/events/evt-does-not-exist


### ============ Validation errors (all expect 400) ============

### Missing everything
POST http://localhost:8080/events
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Negative amount
POST http://localhost:8080/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt-bad-1",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "DEBIT",
  "amount": -10.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:02:11Z"
}

### Unknown type
POST http://localhost:8080/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt-bad-2",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "TRANSFER",
  "amount": 10.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "2026-05-15T14:02:11Z"
}

### Bad timestamp
POST http://localhost:8080/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt-bad-3",
  "accountId": "acct-123",
  "type": "CREDIT",
  "amount": 10.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "eventTimestamp": "not-a-date"
}
